,"value":"\n\n\n\nWhile I've been [converting my blog to use the new MyST engine](./mystmd-with-the-blog.md), I discovered a useful MyST feature. It's not yet possible to [natively parse Jupyter Markdown outputs as MyST](https://github.com/jupyter-book/mystmd/issues/1026) but there's a workaround if you don't mind generating a temporary file.\n\nThe trick is to _write to a temporary file_","key":"zqDbRU5npe"}],"key":"L6IzgWN4d9"},{"type":"footer","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Date: ","key":"YwCADDp7ed"}],"key":"Sd08HIPEZM"},{"type":"text","value":"November 04, 2024 | ","key":"QrlIrsOWac"},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Author: ","key":"XH3hz4td6b"}],"key":"bBh4PcxC6O"},{"type":"text","value":"Chris Holdgraf","key":"UT8IGhxZgJ"}],"key":"lRxtxMAFJC"}],"urlSource":"/blog/2024/programmatic-myst-with-jupyter","key":"jbxoJLqlpa"},{"type":"card","url":"/blog/2024/mystmd-with-the-blog","children":[{"type":"cardTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Re-building my blog with MySTMD","key":"Y9PbkcHmww"}],"key":"UXgDS6JvEj"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\nWow it has been a long time since I've last-written here. It turns out that having two small children and a very demanding job means you don't have as much time for blogging. But that's a whole different blog post...\n\nI've decided to convert my blog to use the new [MyST","key":"SIrz2SLQNF"}],"key":"L6aT7S71N0"},{"type":"footer","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Date: ","key":"xD911E3fkU"}],"key":"KpjH0Bd3rz"},{"type":"text","value":"November 01, 2024 | ","key":"SdgCAwfrat"},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Author: ","key":"r8f6JWCfB7"}],"key":"w0RDNBRhnE"},{"type":"text","value":"Chris Holdgraf","key":"Alslfli5ZO"}],"key":"Gi1jFvOOOD"}],"urlSource":"/blog/2024/mystmd-with-the-blog","key":"bdpHILQED0"},{"type":"card","url":"/blog/2023/ai-for-good","children":[{"type":"cardTitle","childre