":"text","value":"Chris Holdgraf","key":"JIyquZuT95"}],"key":"ScBT5nZbmN"}],"urlSource":"/blog/2023/social-directive","key":"OKbEU9oeCq"},{"type":"card","url":"/blog/2023/fosdem","children":[{"type":"cardTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Report from FOSDEM23: beautiful chaos in a conference","key":"lNnxtdqtl3"}],"key":"M7vlZ79yTv"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\nI recently attended [FOSDEM 2023](https://fosdem.org/2023/), my first FOSDEM!\nI had heard of the conference before, but hadn't really looked into it too much.\nFortunately, after some urging from friends and social media, I took a deeper look and decided I should join to see what all the fuss was about.\n\nHere are a","key":"nhhAgvcNW5"}],"key":"YyDipOJf5R"},{"type":"footer","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Date: ","key":"zIC4MqJxAR"}],"key":"uzPngeSkcu"},{"type":"text","value":"February 06, 2023 | ","key":"SzYlqCipK4"},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Author: ","key":"aOuPAVKDhl"}],"key":"T4UgtRJouw"},{"type":"text","value":"Chris Holdgraf","key":"jHff2V3QYB"}],"key":"CNptrJRQl3"}],"urlSource":"/blog/2023/fosdem","key":"PKIpOKIv0G"},{"type":"card","url":"/blog/2023/sphinx-add-extensions","children":[{"type":"cardTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bundle extensions with your Sphinx theme","key":"oGX84Vv0lW"}],"key":"okrKzQom2V"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\nSphinx is great because it has a ton of useful extensions that let you grow its functionality.\nHowever, a downside of this is that users have to actually _learn about_ those extensions and activate them manually.\nIt's not hard, but it's a non-trivial amount of discovery work.\n\nOne way to solve this is","key":"jNO4MMqkSn"}],"key":"iMA1QgnLMb"},{"type":"footer","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Date: ","key":"LkVFEotHFr"}],"key":"wU0NUV7vVu"},{"type":"text","value":"January 19, 2023 | ","key